1. Is 'src/soe/PrimeSieve.h' needed in configure.ac?

 AC_CONFIG_FILES([
  Makefile
  src/Makefile
  src/apps/Makefile
  src/apps/console/Makefile
  src/soe/Makefile

  src/soe/PrimeSieve.h
  ])

2. Is the section below needed in configure.ac?

PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR=patsubst(AC_PACKAGE_VERSION, [\..*$], [])
PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR=patsubst(AC_PACKAGE_VERSION, [^.*\.], [])
AC_SUBST(PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR)
AC_SUBST(PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR)
AC_SUBST(PACKAGE_YEAR) 

3. Make ParallelPrimeSieve exception safe and implement cancellation.

   This requires OpenMP 4.0 which will be released in the coming
   months. More precisely I plan the following design: if an exception
   is caught in one thread this thread cancels all other threads using
   the new `#pragma omp cancel' clause from OpenMP 4.0 (and then
   probably rethrow the exception).
